import React from 'react'
import { Card, CardContent, CardActions, Typography } from '@material-ui/core';

const CommonCard = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Card>
                <CardContent>
                    <Typography align="center" variant="h4">Google</Typography>
                    <Typography></Typography>
                </CardContent>
                <CardActions>

                </CardActions>
            </Card>
        </>
    )
}

export default CommonCard
